		<h2 class="major">Setting Things Up</h2>
		<p>Sign up for <a href="https://exercism.io/" target="_blank">Exercism</a> on their website, and select the programming language track of your choice. For each track, you can select either Independent Mode, or Mentor Mode. For now, select Independent Mode, as that gives you access to <em>all</em> the exercises.</p>
	</div>
